quran[9{c,v,t}:
12,70,"jab yousuf un bhaiyon ka samaan ladwanaylaga to is ne apne bhai ke samaan mein apna pyalaa rakh diya phir aik pukarnay walay ne pukaar kar kaha"" ae qaafley walo, tum lau g chor ho """
12,71,"unhon ne palat kar poocha"" tumhari kya cheez khoyi gayi? """
12,72,"sarkari mulazimo ne kaha"" badshah ka pemana hum ko nahi milta"" ( aur un ke jamadaar ne kaha )"" jo shakhs laa kar day ga uss ke liye aik bar-Shutar (ount ka wazan)inaam hai, is ka mein zimma laita hon """
12,73,"un bhaiyon ne kaha"" khuda ki qasam, to log khoob jantay ho ke hum is malik mein fasaad karne nahi aeye hain aur hum choryan karne walay log nahi hain """
12,74,"onhon ne kaha"" acha, agar tumhari baat jhooti niklee to chor ki kya saza hai? """
12,75,"onhon ne kaha"" uss ki saza? jis ke samaan mein se cheez niklay woh aap hi apni saza mein rakh liya jaye, hamaray haan to aisay zaalmon ko saza dainay ka yahi tareeqa hai """
12,76,"tab yousuf ne apne bhai se pehlay unn ki kharjion ki talashi leni shuru ki, phir apne bhai ki kharji se gum shuda cheez bar aamad kar li iss terhan hum ne yousuf ki taied apni tadbeer se ki uss ka yeh kaam nah tha ke badshah ke deen ( yani misar ke Shahi qanoon ) mein apne bhai ko pokarta ila yeh ke Allah hi aisa chahay hum jis ke darjay chahtay hain buland kar dete hain, aur aik ilm rakhnay wala aisa hai jo har sahib ilm se baala tar hai"
12,77,"un bhaiyon ne kaha"" yeh chori kere to kuch taajjub ki baat bhi nahi, is se pehlay is ka bhai ( yousuf ) bhi chori kar chuka hai"" yousuf un ki yeh baat sun kar pi gaya, haqeeqat un par nah kholi bas ( zair lab ) itna keh kar reh gaya ke"" barray hi buray ho tum log, ( mere mun Dur mun mujh par ) jo ilzaam tum laga rahay ho is ki haqeeqat khuda khoob jaanta hai """
12,78,"unhon ne kaha"" ae sardar Zee Iqtidaar ( Aziz ), is ka baap bohat boorha aadmi hai, is ki jagah aap hum mein se kisi ko rakh lijiye, hum aap ko bara hi naik nafs ensaan paate hain """
